      *
      * Varible for
     D P               S              5U 0
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D TIAVDA          S              4
     D TIAVD           S              4  0
     D TITDNA          S              7
     D TITDN           S              7  0
     D STATUS          S              1
     D JSONstring      S          32000
     D Error           S            150

      *get input-string
      /copy syspeds/qrpgsrcpy,prolog3

      * Parse input
     C                   EXSR      Parse
      * Open files etc
     C                   EXSR      INIT
      *
     c                   callp     gethtmlifs(
